      "side": 1,
      "message": "_mm_cvtepi32_pd would imply a format conversion (binary -\u003e IEEE754) which is not what we want. We just need to reinterpret the register here. Internally it\u0027s just xmm0, whether the content is double or int. Note that _mm_storel_pd doesn\u0027t care about rounding, denormalization, (or alignment even), which is fortunate.",
